<h1 id="toc30"><span><a href="/three-moons-initiative-hub">The Three Moons Initiative</a></span></h1>
<div class="image-container floatright"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/groups-of-interest/ThreeMoons.jpg" width="60px" alt="ThreeMoons.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<p><strong>Overview:</strong> The Three Moons Initiative is an extradimensional human military organization based in SCP-2922-C, an afterlife also known as Corbenic. Through a partnership with the Corbenese deity JALAKÅRA, they act as a multi-dimensional security force for the protection of the human race.</p>
<p>While Initiative personnel believe that they're operating in humankind's best interests, military overreach, poor communication, issues with internal bureaucracy, and other factors — combined with their disproportionately high military strength to our own — have made them a potential liability to public safety in our dimension.</p>
<p>As such, they maintain an unstable peace with the Foundation. Operatives of the Three Moons Initiative are to be treated with extreme caution.</p>
